{
  "stem": "18572.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we went into the woods, because we heard that there were Jews in the woods and he wasn't gonna keep us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He started talking in terms that the police were coming around, that other people-- that it was dangerous for him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we left and went into the woods.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I think we stayed in the woods from that spring up to the following winter.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the woods-- I have to go back to that part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was-- we were just living off the land.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes I think about it, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I try to realize how did we live.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we just ate berries and other things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think during the night, some of the adults would go into the farms and forage for vegetables.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were always-- we were still cold and hungry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one-- one of my memories is the fact that one time, it rained very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I was sleeping.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I must've rolled down the hill-- there-- we were, like, on some sort of a hill-- because I woke up and I was all by myself.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I woke up and I realized that-- you know, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother must have found me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we were just living in the woods.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "During this time, I-- I suffered from dysentery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I also had these horrible scabs and wounds on my knees, so that there was a period when I couldn't walk, and my mother had to carry me everywhere on her back.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I had these terrible scars and wounds on my knees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And also, the Ukrainians would come into the forest.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The German army did not come into the forest, but the Ukrainians came in and would raid these groups of people.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
